              <p class="text-xs text-lune-faint">Estimated savings / month</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white" id="mt-est-payback">—</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-lune-faint">Payback</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- WJ48 — short caveat, right next to the numbers (distinct from
               the longer methodology note below). -->
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs italic text-lune-faint">
            Preliminary estimate, refined after a site visit.
          </p>
          <p id="mt-estimate-note" class="mt-4 text-xs text-lune-faint">
            Preliminary range calculated from your bill (self-consumption, law 82-21). The
            exact figure is established after a technical site visit — with no obligation.
