          <p class="mt-1 text-xs">
            <a href="/en/methodologie-estimation" class="text-brass-300 underline-offset-2 hover:underline">See how we calculate this estimate</a>
          </p>
          <!-- W342 — "the installation closest to you": computed client-side
               (haversine over REALISATIONS, lib/realisations.ts) from the GPS
